                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/behat/edit/behat3/knpu/suites.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>When Behat loads, it reads step definitions from <code>FeatureContext</code> and <code>MinkContext</code>
because of the <code>behat.yml</code> setup:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="fa2929a0ac">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
